author: Amai Ta. Yume
text:
Good evening Rushi-chi! Today was a wonderful stream! What I mean wonderful is the fact that I get to see many kinds of fans that you have. One is giving you a fair fight with you, another one was secretly trying to help you but he won anyways, another player was outright helping you by killing himself (lol), another one was secretly giving the win to you and you won, another player gave a fair fight and you won against him which is great! Another one who totally BMed you and it was funny as heck. You attracted a lot of audience, which included meaning me and I laughed in awe all the time. It's funny seeing a Steve vs Steve fight, I was like "This is so hilarious" and I really can't stop laughing about it. Steve is a great guy, but I don't think he'd be suited in many tournaments, but since this was played for fun, I was so happy seeing you play and trying your best (even you did a lot of mistakes and they were humorous and great by itself because of your character).

Take care Rushi-chi! Love you a lot again. I'm having a lot of concerns in my life as of today, and just seeing you proved to be a remedy to my sorrow. I hope that every thing you do will always be appreciated by the fans, not because they just love you, but because they wanted to see you have fun together with others. Every actions the majority of the fans will support you no matter what. I'll support this channel all I want. Take care Rushi-chi, let everything be a good peaceful night there! <3
